                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2759" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0042</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11234 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">互联网金融助推家电行业开启产融共生之路 ——海尔海融易平台的“小金链”模式创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internet Finance boosts the home appliance industry to achieve symbiosis ——The Innovation Model of &quot;Xiaojinlian&quot; of Haier’ Hairongyi Platform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈雪，巫凯平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">互联网金融；P2P供应链金融模式；家电行业；中小企业；海融易平台；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Internet finance; P2P supply chain mode; Household appliance industry; Small and medium-sized enterprises; Hairongyi Platform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海融易平台是海尔旗下的互联网金融企业，其“小金链”系列产品采用P2P供应链金融模式，凭借海尔集团的品牌影响力，融合业内优质资源，精选了海尔供应链中稳定的上下游中小企业，以P2P的形式将平台上募集的资金直接借给中小企业，满足中小企业在日常经营中的融资需求。本案例在介绍我国P2P金融和供应链金融结合背景的基础上，阐述了海融易平台的发展历程、主要产品、运营模式和风控创新等，有助于启发思考在“互联网+”时代下，为满足上下游中小企业在日常经营过程中的资金需求，海融易平台如何掌握海量上游供应商和下游经销商的信息数据，缓解借贷双方之间的信息不对称，从而帮助家电行业的中小企业走出“融资难”的困境。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Qingdao Hai Rongyi Network Technology Co., Ltd. is Haier&#39;s Internet financial enterprises. The Hairongyi platform founded in 2014, of which products called &quot;Xiaojinlian&quot; are using P2P supply chain financial model. With Haier Group&#39;s brand influence, it integrates the industrial quality resources, selects Haier supply chain in the stable upstream and downstream small and medium enterprises, and raises funds directly in the form of P2P platform for the small and medium enterprises to meet their financing needs in the daily operation. By introducing the background of P2P finance and supply chain finance in China, this paper expounds the development process, main products, operation mode and risk control innovation of Hairongyi Platform. It is helpful to inspire the thought that in the age of &quot;Internet +&quot;, in order to meet the financial needs in the daily business process of upstream and downstream small and medium enterprises, how does Hairongyi Platform master the mass information data of upstream suppliers and downstream distributors to ease the information asymmetry between the borrowers and lenders, and help small and medium enterprises in home appliance industry out of the &quot;financing difficulties&quot; plight.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理经济学》、《公司理财》、《互联网金融》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息不对称的市场  债权融资</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-07</td>
                            </tr>
